WEBVTT


00:01:22.680 --> 00:01:24.319
Then I'll make your storyline

00:01:24.319 --> 00:01:25.400
completely collapse.

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:27.400
And then,

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:28.280
I'll kill you.

00:01:28.599 --> 00:01:30.000
I'll wait for that day.

00:01:46.200 --> 00:01:47.000
Master.

00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:48.799
Why are you here?

00:01:50.799 --> 00:01:53.040
To prevent you from

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:54.560
going astray, of course.

00:02:01.959 --> 00:02:02.760
Zhantian,

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:04.840
the border situation is urgent.

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:05.760
You

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:07.200
can't delay any longer.

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:08.240
Master,

00:02:08.879 --> 00:02:10.000
within three days,

00:02:10.680 --> 00:02:12.879
I will unify Haicheng.

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:20.639
Brother Zhantian,

00:02:21.199 --> 00:02:22.000
you just...

00:02:22.039 --> 00:02:22.840
Lu Chengwen,

00:02:23.439 --> 00:02:24.599
let me tell you,

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:27.759
the four great families

00:02:27.759 --> 00:02:30.080
will soon be in my pocket.

00:02:31.960 --> 00:02:34.560
You and your family

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:36.080
are dead meat.

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:40.159
Fine.

00:02:40.759 --> 00:02:42.000
Then let me tell you too.

00:02:42.439 --> 00:02:43.560
Starting today,

00:02:43.639 --> 00:02:46.000
Haicheng belongs to me, Lu Chengwen.

00:02:46.240 --> 00:02:47.680
You

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:49.039
are dead meat.

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:55.400
Mr. Lu,

00:02:55.560 --> 00:02:57.400
the Leng family's Qianfeng Group suddenly announced

00:02:57.400 --> 00:02:58.800
that Leng Qingqiu has been dismissed,

00:02:58.960 --> 00:03:00.240
and Gu Zhantian is taking over as CEO.

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:02.360
At the same time, many of Qianfeng Group's businesses

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:03.240
have been suspended.

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:04.080
Their stock is plummeting.

00:03:04.159 --> 00:03:05.759
Gu Zhantian's Dongfang Group

00:03:05.759 --> 00:03:07.919
is frantically buying up Qianfeng Group's shares.

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:09.439
Gu Zhantian has made his move.

00:03:12.759 --> 00:03:13.560
Shihan,

00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:15.240
let's also buy Qianfeng Group's shares

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:16.439
to pull the stock price up.

00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:17.479
However much they throw in,

00:03:17.479 --> 00:03:18.400
we'll match it.

00:03:18.479 --> 00:03:19.479
We absolutely cannot let them hold

00:03:19.479 --> 00:03:20.000
Qianfeng Group

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:21.680
shares exceeding fifty percent.

00:03:22.280 --> 00:03:23.080
Okay.

00:03:29.759 --> 00:03:31.000
You dismissed me,

00:03:31.439 --> 00:03:33.039
and you still want my shares?

00:03:33.439 --> 00:03:34.240
In your dreams.

00:03:35.879 --> 00:03:36.680
Dad,

00:03:37.199 --> 00:03:38.960
Qianfeng Group

00:03:38.960 --> 00:03:40.439
can no longer stay in your hands.

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:43.080
Just you?

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:44.759
Do you know

00:03:44.759 --> 00:03:45.800
that behind Dongfang Group

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:47.000
is Gu Zhantian?

00:03:47.400 --> 00:03:49.240
You're simply inviting a wolf into the house!

00:03:49.599 --> 00:03:50.280
Dasheng Group

00:03:50.280 --> 00:03:52.159
also wants to acquire Qianfeng's shares now.

00:03:52.599 --> 00:03:53.400
Next,

00:03:53.479 --> 00:03:55.479
I will work with Brother Chengwen

00:03:55.479 --> 00:03:56.599
to swallow up Qianfeng.

00:03:58.000 --> 00:03:58.800
Qingqiu,

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:01.280
do you think Lu Chengwen will hand Qianfeng

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:02.280
over to you in the end?

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:04.000
He's just using you.

00:04:05.400 --> 00:04:06.800
Throwing yourself at him,

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:08.639
aren't you just being cheap?

00:04:10.840 --> 00:04:11.639
That's right.

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:13.159
I am being cheap.

00:04:13.879 --> 00:04:14.840
If I wasn't cheap,

00:04:15.360 --> 00:04:16.560
how could I be used by you time and time again

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:18.000
as a bargaining chip for profit?

00:04:21.439 --> 00:04:22.240
Dad,

00:04:22.759 --> 00:04:24.000
from now on,

00:04:24.399 --> 00:04:25.439
you are you,

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:26.639
and I am me.

00:04:26.959 --> 00:04:29.000
As for who Qianfeng Group will ultimately listen to,

00:04:29.439 --> 00:04:30.959
let's see what we're both capable of.

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:33.360
You!

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:45.399
Mr. Lu,

00:04:45.639 --> 00:04:46.720
we've acquired 20%

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:48.000
of Qianfeng's shares.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:48.920
While Gu Zhantian's

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:51.000
Oriental Group got 29%.

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:52.720
The remaining 51%

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:54.040
is in the Leng family's hands.

00:04:54.439 --> 00:04:55.800
Of Qianfeng's remaining shares,

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:57.759
Qingqiu holds 20%,

00:04:58.079 --> 00:04:59.800
and Leng Tianhao holds 31%.

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:02.199
Gu Zhantian wants to swallow Qianfeng.

00:05:02.600 --> 00:05:03.560
His next step

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:05.000
will definitely be to target them both.

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:07.399
Mr. Lu,

00:05:07.639 --> 00:05:08.920
why don't

00:05:08.920 --> 00:05:10.279
we swallow Qianfeng?

00:05:13.160 --> 00:05:14.879
Phase one of the Chengnan project has started,

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:16.639
putting a lot of pressure on our cash flow.

00:05:17.279 --> 00:05:19.360
Why don't we swallow Qianfeng now,

00:05:19.439 --> 00:05:20.800
then manipulate the stock market

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:22.040
to drive up Qianfeng's stock price,

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:23.199
and sell off a portion

00:05:23.199 --> 00:05:24.360
to recover some funds?

00:05:36.360 --> 00:05:37.160
No.

00:05:37.439 --> 00:05:39.240
Qianfeng is Qingqiu's life's work.

00:05:39.439 --> 00:05:41.199
She worked so hard to save it.

00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:43.360
I can't do that.

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:44.399
Mr. Lu,

00:05:44.399 --> 00:05:45.879
this is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:47.360
Even if you don't swallow Qianfeng,

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:48.759
someone else will.

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:50.240
At least

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:51.199
if you take it,

00:05:51.199 --> 00:05:53.199
you can do everything to protect Ms. Leng.

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:54.800
It's better than someone else taking it.

00:06:06.279 --> 00:06:07.399
Shihan is right.

00:06:07.759 --> 00:06:09.279
You should swallow Qianfeng.

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:20.439
Rather than letting Gu Zhantian swallow it,

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:22.759
I'd prefer you to acquire Qianfeng.

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:23.959
Qingqiu,

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:25.360
I

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:26.759
have no interest in Qianfeng.

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:27.759
Besides,

00:06:27.759 --> 00:06:28.959
I don't have that much money.

00:06:29.439 --> 00:06:30.519
Furthermore,

00:06:30.519 --> 00:06:32.480
Qianfeng has been your dream for years,

00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:33.959
and your life's work.

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:36.240
I can't.

00:06:36.279 --> 00:06:37.079
You can.

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:38.680
From now on,

00:06:39.480 --> 00:06:40.560
my heart

00:06:40.639 --> 00:06:42.199
and everything I have is yours.

00:06:48.439 --> 00:06:49.439
Chengwen,

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:51.759
swallow Qianfeng.

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:07.800
Chengwen,

00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:10.000
I have no home anymore.

00:08:10.079 --> 00:08:11.759
I don't have Qianfeng either.

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:14.360
I have nothing left.

00:08:19.160 --> 00:08:19.959
Qingqiu,

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:21.519
don't worry.

00:08:22.040 --> 00:08:23.319
If I really

00:08:23.319 --> 00:08:24.360
acquire Qianfeng,

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:25.720
I will give

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:26.639
all the shares I get

00:08:26.639 --> 00:08:27.439
to you.

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:30.759
It's fine.

00:08:32.200 --> 00:08:33.200
Since you've already decided

00:08:33.200 --> 00:08:34.240
to be with me,

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:35.360
then

00:08:35.360 --> 00:08:36.879
what's the difference between yours and mine?

00:08:48.759 --> 00:08:49.600
Lu Chengwen

00:08:50.960 --> 00:08:52.759
And here I thought you wanted to swallow Qianfeng.

00:08:52.759 --> 00:08:53.600
I wanted to help you.

00:08:53.639 --> 00:08:54.399
You've already...

00:08:54.399 --> 00:08:55.000
No.

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:55.480
Already...

00:08:55.480 --> 00:08:56.240
No, no, no.

00:08:56.240 --> 00:08:57.279
I-I didn't eat it!

00:08:57.279 --> 00:08:58.960
Brother Chengwen and I are already together.

00:08:59.240 --> 00:09:00.159
Both Qianfeng and I...

00:09:00.159 --> 00:09:01.000
...are his.

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:06.039
I'm not listening! I'm not listening! I'm not listening!

00:09:06.279 --> 00:09:07.720
Once,

00:09:07.720 --> 00:09:09.600
there was a man who spoiled me unconditionally

00:09:09.679 --> 00:09:11.679
and loved me, standing right in front of me.

00:09:12.440 --> 00:09:13.279
I'm not listening! I'm not listening!

00:09:13.279 --> 00:09:14.559
But I didn't know how to cherish him.

00:09:15.279 --> 00:09:17.200
I almost lost him.

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:19.240
So now,

00:09:20.200 --> 00:09:21.799
even if it costs me everything,

00:09:21.960 --> 00:09:23.440
I will be with him.

00:09:25.559 --> 00:09:26.360
Chengwen.

00:09:30.639 --> 00:09:32.960
Gu Zhantian came to Grandpa to cooperate.

00:09:35.039 --> 00:09:35.720
Gu Zhantian

00:09:35.720 --> 00:09:36.879
went to the old man to cooperate?

00:09:37.039 --> 00:09:37.840
Yes.

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:39.159
He asked Grandpa to help him

00:09:39.159 --> 00:09:40.600
crash Qianfeng Group's stock tomorrow.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:42.960
The reason Grandpa invested 20 billion in the south of the city

00:09:43.039 --> 00:09:44.440
was because he was deceived by you.

00:09:44.679 --> 00:09:45.559
Just like

00:09:45.559 --> 00:09:47.039
how he was deceived by you back then.

00:09:47.759 --> 00:09:48.559
It seems

00:09:48.840 --> 00:09:49.960
Gu Zhantian's plan

00:09:49.960 --> 00:09:51.440
is to swallow the four major families.

00:09:51.559 --> 00:09:53.000
After he takes down Qianfeng,

00:09:53.200 --> 00:09:54.679
the Chen family will be next.

00:09:56.279 --> 00:09:57.639
The old man is being foolish!

00:09:58.200 --> 00:09:58.759
So,

00:09:58.759 --> 00:10:00.000
Qianfeng Group

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:01.000
is the deciding factor.

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:02.000
Exactly.

00:10:02.360 --> 00:10:03.159
Xuejiao,

00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:04.840
go back and tell your dad

00:10:04.879 --> 00:10:06.559
that there might be a tough battle tomorrow.

00:10:14.200 --> 00:10:16.639
Right now,

00:10:16.639 --> 00:10:18.360
it all depends on whether we can hold on tomorrow.

00:10:27.200 --> 00:10:28.000
Brother Chengwen,

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:29.399
the 5 billion you gave me last time,

00:10:29.399 --> 00:10:30.879
and Gu Zhantian's 5 billion,

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:32.279
I've invested it all.

00:10:32.399 --> 00:10:33.559
That money should be

00:10:33.559 --> 00:10:34.799
almost depleted by now.

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:36.759
The rest is up to us.

00:10:42.399 --> 00:10:42.759
Hello?

00:10:42.879 --> 00:10:43.720
Hello, Chengwen.

00:10:44.159 --> 00:10:45.919
Gu Zhantian has already left for the Leng family.

00:10:45.960 --> 00:10:46.759
That fast?

00:10:48.279 --> 00:10:49.240
I got it.

00:10:51.200 --> 00:10:52.440
Gu Zhantian went to the Leng family.

00:10:52.639 --> 00:10:54.399
He's probably going to discuss with Leng Tianhao

00:10:54.399 --> 00:10:55.440
to negotiate a cooperation.

00:10:56.399 --> 00:10:58.159
Is he that certain he can win?

00:10:58.559 --> 00:10:59.639
Negotiations

00:10:59.639 --> 00:11:00.840
can happen without needing to win.

00:11:01.159 --> 00:11:01.559
On our side,

00:11:01.559 --> 00:11:03.399
showing just a little weakness is enough.

00:11:03.759 --> 00:11:05.399
The capital pool of Dasheng Group

00:11:05.399 --> 00:11:06.559
is basically an open book now.

00:11:06.559 --> 00:11:08.200
But as for Gu Zhantian's funds,

00:11:08.360 --> 00:11:09.399
we're still not clear.

00:11:10.799 --> 00:11:11.559
Qingqiu,

00:11:11.559 --> 00:11:12.720
you and Xuejiao stay here

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:13.480
and coordinate with each other.

00:11:13.879 --> 00:11:14.600
Shihan, come with me.

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:15.960
Tell her anytime if you have any problems.

00:11:15.960 --> 00:11:16.759
Where are you going?

00:11:17.159 --> 00:11:18.399
Isn't it just a negotiation?

00:11:18.440 --> 00:11:19.279
I can do that too.

00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:30.000
Gu Zhantian,

00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:32.159
To think I trusted you so much.

00:11:32.399 --> 00:11:34.000
You actually want to swallow Qianfeng!

00:11:44.679 --> 00:11:46.360
I'm doing this for your own good.

00:11:46.840 --> 00:11:48.200
The business world is like a battlefield.

00:11:48.639 --> 00:11:50.039
Once your thinking ages,

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:51.159
you are not far

00:11:51.159 --> 00:11:52.000
from death.

00:11:52.600 --> 00:11:53.759
I advise you

00:11:54.200 --> 00:11:56.039
to sign the contract quickly.

00:11:57.080 --> 00:11:58.440
While Qianfeng's stock price

00:11:58.440 --> 00:12:00.200
hasn't been completely crashed yet,

00:12:00.960 --> 00:12:02.360
save some money for your retirement.

00:12:02.960 --> 00:12:03.840
Gu Zhantian!

00:12:04.440 --> 00:12:05.240
You...